gui.butterflies.fact.emperor: Emperor butterflies like to eat tree sap.
gui.butterflies.fact.forester: This pink butterfly isn't scared of cats.
gui.butterflies.fact.glasswing: Glasswings can be hard to spot for predators.
gui.butterflies.fact.green-skirt-baron: Very little is known about this butterfly.
gui.butterflies.fact.hairstreak: Hairstreaks like to choose a tree to be their home.
gui.butterflies.fact.heath: Heath butterflies dislike the dark and like to stay low.
gui.butterflies.fact.hummingbird: These moths are active during the day.
gui.butterflies.fact.ice: Ice butterflies have evolved to be able to move when frozen.
gui.butterflies.fact.indianmeal: Indian Meal moths like to eat grain.
gui.butterflies.fact.lava: Lava moths cannot be caught with a butterfly net.
gui.butterflies.fact.light: These are said to be the spirits of the dead.
gui.butterflies.fact.longwing: A longwing's lifespan is as long as its wings.
gui.butterflies.fact.luna: Their green larvae will make clicking noises when threatened.
gui.butterflies.fact.morpho: A morpho's blue colour comes from tiny scales on its wings.
gui.butterflies.fact.oak-silk: This moth is primarily known for producing white, hard, and elastic silk.
gui.butterflies.fact.peacock: Peacock butterflies like to fly around stinging nettles.

gui.butterflies.fact.peacock-pansy-wet: Peacock Pansies look different depending on the season.
gui.butterflies.fact.peppered: These moths use wood as camouflage.
gui.butterflies.fact.rainbow: Rainbow butterflies have only been recently discovered.
gui.butterflies.fact.spongy: Female spongy moths don't fly well.
gui.butterflies.fact.spongymale: Spongy moths are destructive to foliage.
gui.butterflies.fact.swallowtail: Swallowtails are the largest butterflies in the world.
gui.butterflies.zhuangzi:
As I flutter in the breeze
I think of what my mind's eye sees
At night when I'm an old wise man
Contemplating the things I can.
Am I the one that dreams of he,
Or is he the one that dreams of me?

- 莊子
